Package: PDM
Type: Package
Title: Principal Direction of Mediation
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-07-17
Author: Oliver Chen
Maintainer: Oliver Chen <oliver@jhmi.edu>
Imports: MASS
Description: Given treatment, response, and mediation matrix, this package provides functions that resturns the estimates of the Principal Direction of Mediations (PDMs) and corresponding path coefficients.
